Bini Smaghi Says ECB Will Make Sure Enough Liquidity in Market

-- B y   G a b i   T h e s i n g     a n d   S a n d r i n e   R a s t e l l o
-- 
2011-09-25T13:02:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-25/bini-smaghi-says-ecb-will-make-sure-enough-liquidity-in-market.html
European Central Bank Executive
Board member Lorenzo  Bini Smaghi  reiterated that the central
bank will ensure that “there is enough liquidity” in the
market.  As long as banks have enough collateral they can access the
ECB’s refinancing operations and the “amount of collateral is
huge,” Bini Smaghi said in a panel discussion in  Washington 
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gabi Thesing at 
 gthesing@bloomberg.net  